lead_paragraph: Among the debatable calls in the NFL's Week 15, none backfired more than Andy Reid's attempt to ice an already frozen kicker at Arrowhead Stadium.

headline.print_headline: AP Analysis: Andy Reid's Ice-The-Kicker Strategy Backfired
